{"name": "The Chateau of Champagne", "location": "Grand-Est", "guests": "120 guests", "sleeps": "Paris, 105min/150km", "from": "\u20ac From 3,300", "timestamp": 1669375009.2309656, "description": "DESCRIPTION\nThis Ch\u00e2teau is located in the heart of Champagne and provides a stunning backdrop to your celebrations in a prestigious location.\nHost your vin d'honneur in a typical Champenoise cellar, enjoy a ceremony in the 4 hectares of pristine parkland and celebration with a wedding reception within the Chateau's reception rooms or out on the lawn - the choice is yours.\nIn total the Chateau has 3 living rooms on the first floor and can accommodate up to 120 guests.\nRoom capacity\nThe Cellar located under the Castle boasts a warm and atmospheric ambience.\nThe Salons located on the ground floor of the Ch\u00e2teau are in a row and spread over the entire surface of the Ch\u00e2teau (for a total surface area greater than 120 m\u00b2). This means that the rooms can be used individually for more intimate occasions, or all together for larger affairs.\nThe Ros\u00e9 Room located on the 1st floor will welcome you with a view overlooking the Park of the Castle. Suitable for up to 40 guests.\nThe Cave Comtesse overlooking the 4 hectares of the Ch\u00e2teau will typically remind you of the atmosphere of Champagne cellars. Suitable for up to 88 guests, ideal for a cocktail hour if the weather is not suitable to be outside.\nComplete packages are available which include privatisation of the venue, dining, wine and, of course, champagne. The talented chefs can offer you different menus depending on the season and your preferences and style.\nNearby Accommodation\nThere is plenty of accommodation nearby, including sumptuous hotels and traditional gites. Transfers can be arranged through the Chateau and you can choose to get ready in the Chateau itself if you so wish.\nThe Ch\u00e2teau, a work of the 19th century, will welcome you for your special day. If you dreamed of a majestic and elegant ceremony, the estate is made for you. A dream come true!\nGastronomy\nYou will have the chance to taste champagnes, wines and spirits with amazing notes at the Ch\u00e2teau. Take advantage of the reputation of this place to introduce your guests to the charm and beauty it can offer you. A full catering kitchen is available and you can choose your own caterers or the Chateau can provide exceptional menus.\nWe look forward to hearing from you and we will be delighted to welcome you to the Chateau.", "images": ["https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/white-and-beige-placesetting.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/a_chateau_comtesse_lafond_epernay_france_wedding_-_the_overwhelmed_bride_wedding_ideas_blog_11_.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/a_chateau_comtesse_lafond_epernay_france_wedding_-_the_overwhelmed_bride_wedding_ideas_blog_1.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/photo_ladoucette_967-large.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/306444497_507309848067787_4856195576726728756_n.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/0071_m_j_202899.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/a_chateau_comtesse_lafond_epernay_france_wedding_-_the_overwhelmed_bride_wedding_ideas_blog_1_.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/a_chateau_comtesse_lafond_epernay_france_wedding_-_the_overwhelmed_bride_wedding_ideas_blog_2_.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/306157025_507309854734453_1879339148481511445_n.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/306162423_507309841401121_2965913142095382822_n.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/499/large/a_chateau_comtesse_lafond_epernay_france_wedding_-_the_overwhelmed_bride_wedding_ideas_blog_7_.jpg", "https://www.frenc